==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Lather
<hw>Lath"er</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To form lather, or a froth like
lather; to accumulate foam from profuse sweating, as a horse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lather</ent>⟦br⟧

